text: "Latch" is a song by English garage house duo Disclosure by English singer Sam Smith. It was released as a digital download on 8 October 2012. It was the lead single from their debut studio album, Settle (2013). It was on the UK Singles Chart at number 26 and has peaked at number 11."Watch: Disclosure Reveal New Video For ‘Latch’ ", This Is Fake DIY, 9 October 2012, retrieved 30 October 2012 ==References== Category:2012 songs Category:Sam Smith songs
